          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We believe effective products should never force a choice between nature and performance. <br/><br/>More than 83% of our ingredients are derived from natural origin. The remaining percentage consists of carefully selected high-performance ingredients that help maximise efficacy, stability and safety.<br/><br/>Every ingredient earns its place in the formula. Nothing unnecessary. Nothing added for trend or appearance alone.<br/><br/>Free from sulfates, parabens, synthetic fragrances and unnecessary fillers - only what your skin needs, and nothing it doesn't.</p>",
